{d}nin-ŋir₂-su₂ ur-saŋ {d}en-lilₓ(E₂)-ra\gen\dat e₂-an-na-tum₂ ensi₂ lagaš{ki}-ke₄ šag₄ kug-ge
5el3 pad₃-da {d}nanše nin uru₁₆-na-ke₄ kur\l3 gu₂\abs ŋar-ŋar {d}nin-ŋir₂-su₂-ka-ke₄ dumu aya₂-kur-gal ensi₂ lagaš{ki}-ka-ke₄ umma{ki} gu₂-eden-na\abs ba-de₆-a\abs mu-ha-lam-ma-a\l1 {d}nin-ŋir₂-su₂-ra
5ral2 {a-šag₄}ašag ki\abs aŋ₂-ni gu₂-eden-na\abs šu-na
5al2 mu-ni-gi₄ ki-sur-ra gu₂-gu₂ ŋir₂-su₂{ki}-ka\abs {d}nin-ŋir₂-su₂-ra
5ral2 šu-na
5al2 mu-ni-gi₄-a
5al2 lum-ma\abs ŋir₂-nun-ta šag₄ kug-ge
5el3 pad₃-da mu	erm mu-na-še₂₁ x arad₂ x x a\abs mu-na-ru
